title: Women's Health: Part I
itunes:title: Women's Health: Part I
description: Daniel speaks with Dr. Laurie Zephyrin, VP of Health Systems Equity at the Commonwealth Fund. Laurie was a key player in transforming women’s health at the VA, having trained as an OB-GYN before scaling her attention to systems, structures and culture.
